Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.10,0:02:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.80,0:03:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 看到哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.00,0:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书店 有好多旧书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧书店啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店名是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.40,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个怎样的书店 有些什么样的书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样的书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画 小说 外文书什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.20,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不语我怎么能知道啊 只有书名也行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是些大人看的杂志吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说中了啊 原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.90,0:03:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着好多H书的书店啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一你这白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.48,0:04:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an4\fn@幼圆}新店开张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.92,0:04:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫看见的是个摆着许多低级的书的旧书店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边是个老旧的咖啡厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.00,0:04:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店主是个带着鹦鹉长得像癞蛤蟆老头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那店到底在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子到底想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐到底要做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.17,0:04:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 出现万一的情况我们就把那男的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.72,0:05:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 确实像癞蛤蟆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.49,0:05:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便问问吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.88,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.37,0:05:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭和40年之前的这类杂志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店基本还有存货
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是地狱通信我完全没有印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候的书呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 没有就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.54,0:06:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个汉字为书名的书几乎哪个时代都有不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.85,0:06:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封面是什么样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是写实风格还是迷幻风格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是穿衣服还是不穿衣服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是我记错了 忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人和地狱通信没有关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我感觉应该有什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那只鸟怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑 太可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人和鸟 哪个才是本体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说什么啊 要振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.38,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱为什么要来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.84,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天是不是有个女孩来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 熟人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.85,0:06:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 看到她进了这个店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这里干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浏览了一下 那旁书架上的书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前偶然也来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似是优等生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兴趣就进来看看的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.04,0:07:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是头一会看见那么漂亮的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.12,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道炼狱通信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.85,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天 一个老朋友跟我这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的杀意无法抑制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.67,0:07:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于将寄往炼狱通信的信封
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放进了信箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霎时间 感到了背后有什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛回头间看到一个美丽动人而又楚楚可怜的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼狱少女就站在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽动人而又楚楚可怜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登录地狱通信的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女就会帮你消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和故事里说的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要寄出炼狱通信的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼狱少女就会帮你消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.47,0:08:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是这个故事已经是50多年前写的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.99,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是偶然的一致吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\fn@幼圆\pos(514,116)}图    文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者名与下地狱的发音相似
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺石雄智朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺石雄智朗　寺石雄智朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.59,0:08:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.12,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才在找的不是杂志而是这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.89,0:08:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.99,0:08:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事 他还有其他作品吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.40,0:08:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这类杂志投稿的很多人会用多个笔名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是每个笔名只用一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.40,0:09:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺石雄智朗 图和文章都是他写的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.92,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅画虽说是福元的风格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其它的完全不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.90,0:09:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 也许是许多人共同创作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.09,0:09:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个是《肉与樱》啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当时的主编还活着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫宫部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是刚才来电话的柴田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 客人来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.15,0:09:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是柴田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要和我谈谈《肉与樱》吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺石雄智朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.69,0:10:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 说的是炼狱通信的作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是福元先生写的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.90,0:10:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时在我们这里画杂志封面和插画的画家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出过故事的也只有这一部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是江黑堂的店主说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然其中一幅是福元的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.40,0:10:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其它都不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.31,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他特意改变画风的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.21,0:10:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.07,0:10:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是有一次作家们去热海旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边的就是福元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个批斗篷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.62,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 然后旁边的就是大河内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是当时我们的头号作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和福元是搭档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人私下似乎交情也很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这之后不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河内就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.86,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大河内死得太突然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们因为怎么填补他的空缺起了很大的争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.90,0:11:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这时福元带着那篇稿子出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从内容来说有些不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是已经没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.79,0:11:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了赶着截稿日期就姑且登载了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过外界评价并不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.67,0:11:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论故事还是插画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都和我们风格不符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.22,0:11:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是炼狱少女过于清秀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.48,0:11:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.80,0:11:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来这里准备了别的插画的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我换掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了福元从前的作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画本身可是很出色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和杂志风格不合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也许是他平生最高的杰作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.79,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是本来的炼狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.50,0:12:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.98,0:12:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼狱通信的主人公是杂志的插画家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个漂亮的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.53,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天当红作家“大”染指了他的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.53,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}“大”暗指大河内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她因此自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.41,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人公因此对“大”萌生了巨大的杀意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.54,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.67,0:12:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元的妻子真是位美丽的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一天突然自杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀的理由不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元也什么都没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后不久大河内就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是死因不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.68,0:12:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相似啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子自杀后朋友也死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和故事情节简直一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是从两人的死中迸发的灵感吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元先生现在在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.01,0:13:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道他是活着还是死了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.30,0:13:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后因为出版条例等限制这个行业也冷清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.17,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也听说过福元去了某处画电影广告牌的传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意是50年前的地址的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年 小镇的样子一定变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.56,0:13:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元还会在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这更大的变化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇已经没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.75,0:14:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然四处散布着民宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.31,0:14:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已经再也不能称为小镇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是商社的破旧公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和废楼没啥两样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.20,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.83,0:14:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元先生 福元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元先生 您在里面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.78,0:14:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想跟您说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.85,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.16,0:15:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟您谈一下这个女孩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.47,0:15:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的作品 炼狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我在现实中见过这个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称作地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.97,0:15:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有多少时日了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被无聊的事烦到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.48,0:15:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.61,0:15:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全身都是毛病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.02,0:15:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天暴毙也不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就单刀直入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.40,0:15:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您曾经见过地狱少女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是您的亲身经历吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么蠢话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道她是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有她为什么要这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个叫地狱通信的主页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说在那里写下怨恨的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨就会消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.59,0:16:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多年轻人都在登录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多人失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 我都要阻止这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.21,0:16:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的年代是报纸的寻人栏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从大河内那里听说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.24,0:16:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说过地狱通讯的传言吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要寄信给地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就能替你消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.25,0:17:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系地址写在报纸寻人栏的空白处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.04,0:17:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若不是胸怀执怨便看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.72,0:17:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时觉得这事件和我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.04,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.64,0:17:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有生以来第一次真的想杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我这样想的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.98,0:17:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1700,0)}君之怨恨 愿为消之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.96,0:17:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都如那里所写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 怨恨若被消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.52,0:18:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后你的灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这就是所谓那代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往地狱的刻印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.60,0:18:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约时我觉得那还是很久以后的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.89,0:18:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来 我的人生就是和这刻印的斗争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了忘记刻印的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.93,0:18:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经拼命工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.32,0:18:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾通过修行寻求救赎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.76,0:18:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自暴自弃投身于赌博
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.76,0:18:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾想稍微为世人付出 参加志愿者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.66,0:19:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无论做什么心灵都得不到解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.02,0:19:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个刻印提醒着我的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.30,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是死后坠入地狱 永远在苦痛中延续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.57,0:19:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看看我最后的作品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.11,0:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了地狱的话 也许还能见到这女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.23,0:19:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我唯一的期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.81,0:19:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待 她毁了你的人生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁了我的人生的是大河内啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.70,0:20:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.97,0:20:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时大河内带着防身的手枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.60,0:20:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我自己想为妻子报仇的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.26,0:20:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许反会被他杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感谢她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么人 地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是人外之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.82,0:20:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也许曾经是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.80,0:20:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看江户时代中期书籍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有关于地狱少女的记述
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.79,0:20:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 更早一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许能到安土桃山时代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么您会写炼狱通信这个故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.41,0:20:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许不是我 而是她的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.73,0:21:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 必须向谁来传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向谁传达 那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.66,0:21:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.92,0:21:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.40,0:22:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.42,0:22:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.93,0:22:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.42,0:22:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.67,0:22:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在地狱能和大河内见面了吧
